OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy and breezy for
OL,6,Fcentral and southern areas, with
OL,7,Fshowery rain possible in the
OL,8,Fsoutheast. Wet and windy weather
OL,9,Fdeveloping across northern Scotland. A
OL,10,Ffine day for many elsewhere with sunny
OL,11,Fspells. Feeling cooler than Saturday
OL,12,Ffor most.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FEvening rain across Scotland
OL,15,Fmoving south to reach central areas by
OL,16,Fdawn. Wintry showers following into
OL,17,FScotland. Clear spells otherwise, but
OL,18,Fturning cold for the time of year with
OL,19,Ffrost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
