OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FCloud and rain continues
OL,6,Fsouthwards, clearing the UK into the
OL,7,Fevening. Sunny spells elsewhere, but a
OL,8,Ffew showers over northern Scotland and
OL,9,Feastern coasts of England, where
OL,10,Fbreezy. Below-average temperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
